channel.title: [DEV] iHaxx [DEV]
channel.description:
[center]Hey, back in summer 2007 i owned the server named EluxScape which then moved the name JavaScape. The server closed around september 2007 when i got my new laptop as i could no longer be bothered with the server. In November 2007 i moved on to habbo retros and became one of the most popular retros out. iHaxx Hotel, which was ranked 3rd on the of the most popular topsites. I've recently been bored and wanted to move back to RuneScape servers for good. Which means i'm going to need a little bit of help ;)
I'm currently looking for someone who can help setup a webclient for the site which will be hosted at http://www.iHaxx.net the server will be called iHaxx with out the scape at the end :) i like to keep my names original. I'm also looking for people to help code the server and all the other crap with it :p
Intrested? Post a reply with some details i can contact you on or just simply add my msn Diesel@iHaxx.Net
Thanks, Elux :D[/center]
